Control Center Control Center Notification Shade
This service allows to use the private settings panel by swiping down from the top edge of the screen. The data collected from this service is not saved, collected or used in any way. The uses are outlined below. This service does not send your data to 3rd parties over the internet. \n\nPermission: \n\n- Track your actions: Get feedback from the system when the top edge of the screen is touched to activate the settings panel. \n\n- Get window info: Necessary to automatically hit some settings after the user set them to enable and disable them in the application\'s provided interface.
